item.name: Ball Valve
item.description: Allows fluid to flow in one direction only

item.name: Gate Valve
item.description: Allows fluid to flow in both directions

item.name: Globe Valve
item.description: Allows fluid to flow in both directions, but with more control than a gate valve

item.name: Socket Weld Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that is used to connect two pipes that have a socket welded end.

item.name: Threaded Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that has threads on both ends, which allows it to be screwed into another fitting or a pipe.

item.name: Compression Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that uses a compression ring to seal the connection between two pipes.

item.name: Flange Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that has a flange on one or both ends, which allows it to be bolted to another fitting or a pipe.

item.name: Yoke Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that has a yoke on one end, which allows it to be connected to a valve or other device.

item.name: Union Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that allows two pipes to be easily disconnected and reconnected.

item.name: Hose Barb Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that has a hose barb on one end, which allows it to be connected to a hose.

item.name: Slip-on Fitting
item.description: A type of fitting that is slipped over a pipe and then welded in place.

item.name: Blind Flange
item.description: A type of flange that is used to seal the end of a pipe.
